    "intro3": "We focus on building programming thinking - from Fullstack, DevOps, Security to Solution Architect - with a clear and practical roadmap.",
    "diff": {
      "title": "What makes StarCi Academy different?",
      "des1": "StarCi Academy focuses on the essence of the IT industry. We don't just teach knowledge, but also train standard programming thinking and system design skills - core competencies that help you develop sustainably in the AI era.",
      "des2": "Thinking before stack",
      "des3": "Technology changes constantly and knowledge is everywhere. We focus on teaching the fundamentals, keywords, and thinking skills so that after the course, you can research, read docs, and expand on any stack you want.",
